        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Recognizing the Role of Direct Support Professionals Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of Management and Budget to establish a separate category within the Standard Occupational Classification system for direct support professionals (i.e., individuals who provide services to promote independence in individuals with a disability) for data reporting purposes. </p>]]>
        </text>
